import React from 'react'; import { resumeData } from '../data/resumeData'; import './Wireframe1.css'; const Wireframe1 = () => { const { personalInfo, summary, skills, experience, education, projects, certifications } = resumeData; return (
{/* Header Section */}

{personalInfo.name}

{personalInfo.title}

{personalInfo.email} • {personalInfo.phone} • {personalInfo.location}
{/* Summary Section */}

Summary

{summary}

{/* Skills Section */}

Skills

Programming Languages

{skills.programming.map((skill, index) => ( {skill} ))}

Frontend

{skills.frontend.map((skill, index) => ( {skill} ))}

Backend

{skills.backend.map((skill, index) => ( {skill} ))}

Tools & Technologies

{skills.tools.map((skill, index) => ( {skill} ))}
{/* Experience Section */}

Professional Experience

{experience.map((job, index) => (

{job.title}

{job.company} {job.period}

{job.location}

{job.description}

    {job.achievements.map((achievement, achIndex) => (
  • {achievement}
    • ))}
))}
{/* Education Section */}

Education

{education.map((edu, index) => (

{edu.degree}

{edu.institution}

{edu.location}

{edu.period}

GPA: {edu.gpa}

Relevant Coursework: {edu.relevantCoursework.join(', ')}

))}
{/* Projects Section */}

Projects

{projects.map((project, index) => (

{project.name}

{project.description}

Technologies: {project.technologies.join(', ')}

{project.period}

GitHub: {project.link}

    {project.features.map((feature, featIndex) => (
  • {feature}
    • ))}
))}
{/* Certifications Section */}

Certifications

{certifications.map((cert, index) => (

{cert.name}

{cert.issuer}

{cert.date}

ID: {cert.credentialId}

))}
); }; export default Wireframe1;
